Slide: Vision & Mission (Innovation Track)

Vision
Create a BU where every associate can convert real problems into measurable business impact.

Mission
Use Eureka + Track SPOCs as a repeatable operating system to:

Capture ideas aligned to BU priorities

Evaluate value & feasibility consistently

Validate quickly through time-boxed experiments

Scale winners to pilot/production with clear ownership

Measure & reuse outcomes across teams

Slide: Activities to Improve Innovation Culture

Lower friction: templates, examples, SPOC office hours, fast triage

Create momentum: fortnightly reviews + monthly demo/decision forum

Cross-track collaboration: Engineering + AI + AACI squads for top ideas

Recognition & growth: awards, visibility, and career signal for contributors

Leadership enablement: clear priority themes, quick decisions, unblock dependencies, and a defined path to production
